text: Mahmoud Younis (; April 12, 1911 - April 18, 1976) was an engineer of the Suez Canal nationalization on July 26, 1956. He served as Chairman of the Suez Canal Authority (July 10, 1957 – October 10, 1965). Category:1911 births Category:1976 deaths Category:People of the Suez Crisis Category:People from Cairo
title: Mahmoud Younis
